One of Maui's popular vacation spots, Papakea is well known for the many amenities that are available to owners and visitors that include two separate spacious pool areas with BBQs, two covered clubhouses that are available for entertaining your guests, two large jacuzzis, two putting greens, and on site security make this vacation destination a highly sought after place. Lush tropical landscaping and Koi fish ponds are trademarks of Papakea. Located just north of the famous Kaanapali Beach Papakea is close to shopping, beaches, and restaurants.
